  "id": "api/index/const/asapScheduler",
  "title": "asapScheduler",
  "contents": "\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"page-actions\">\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/reactivex/rxjs/edit/master/src/internal/scheduler/asap.ts?message=docs(index)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L55-L54\" aria-label=\"編輯建議\" title=\"編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/reactivex/rxjs/tree/7.5.2/src/internal/scheduler/asap.ts#L55-L54\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n  </div>\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/index\", \"name\": \"rxjs/index\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/index/const/asapScheduler\", \"name\": \"asapScheduler\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n      <a href=\"/api\">API</a> / <a href=\"api/index\">rxjs/index</a>\n    </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"asapscheduler\">asapScheduler<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/index/const/asapScheduler#asapscheduler\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label const\">const</label>\n    \n    \n    <label class=\"api-status-label stable\">穩定</label>\n    \n    \n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  \n\n  <p class=\"short-description\"></p><p translation-result=\"on\">越快越好（as soon as possible）排程器</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Asap Scheduler</p>\n\n<p></p>\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">\n  const <a href=\"api/index/const/asapScheduler\" class=\"code-anchor\">asapScheduler</a>: AsapScheduler;\n  </code-example>\n\n  \n  \n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/index/const/asapScheduler#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p translation-result=\"on\"><span class=\"informal\">儘可能快地執行任務，因為它可以非同步執行</span></p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><span class=\"informal\">Perform task as fast as it can be performed asynchronously</span></p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">當你使用 <code><a href=\"api/index/const/asap\" class=\"code-anchor\">asap</a></code> 排程器來延遲任務時，它的行為與 <a href=\"api/index/const/asyncScheduler\"><code>asyncScheduler</code></a> 排程器相同。但是，如果你將延遲設定為 <code>0</code>，則 <code><a href=\"api/index/const/asap\" class=\"code-anchor\">asap</a></code> 將等待當前同步執行的程式碼結束，然後嘗試儘快執行給定的任務。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><code><a href=\"api/index/const/asap\" class=\"code-anchor\">asap</a></code> scheduler behaves the same as <a href=\"api/index/const/asyncScheduler\"><code>asyncScheduler</code></a> scheduler when you use it to delay task\nin time. If however you set delay to <code>0</code>, <code><a href=\"api/index/const/asap\" class=\"code-anchor\">asap</a></code> will wait for current synchronously executing\ncode to end and then it will try to execute given task as fast as possible.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><code><a href=\"api/index/const/asap\" class=\"code-anchor\">asap</a></code> 排程器將盡最大努力減少當前執行程式碼結束和計劃任務開始之間的時間。這使它成為執行所謂『延遲』的最佳候選者。傳統上，這是透過呼叫 <code>setTimeout(deferredTask, 0)</code> 來實現的，但是該技術會引入一些不必要的延遲（儘管很小）。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><code><a href=\"api/index/const/asap\" class=\"code-anchor\">asap</a></code> scheduler will do its best to minimize time between end of currently executing code\nand start of scheduled task. This makes it best candidate for performing so called \"deferring\".\nTraditionally this was achieved by calling <code>setTimeout(deferredTask, 0)</code>, but that technique involves\nsome (although minimal) unwanted delay.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">請注意，使用 <code><a href=\"api/index/const/asap\" class=\"code-anchor\">asap</a></code> 排程器並不一定意味著你的任務將在當前執行程式碼之後首先處理。特別是，如果之前還用 <code><a href=\"api/index/const/asap\" class=\"code-anchor\">asap</a></code> 安排了某個任務，則那個任務將首先執行。話雖如此，如果你需要非同步排程任務，而且希望越快越好，那麼 <code><a href=\"api/index/const/asap\" class=\"code-anchor\">asap</a></code> scheduler 會是你最好的選擇。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Note that using <code><a href=\"api/index/const/asap\" class=\"code-anchor\">asap</a></code> scheduler does not necessarily mean that your task will be first to process\nafter currently executing code. In particular, if some task was also scheduled with <code><a href=\"api/index/const/asap\" class=\"code-anchor\">asap</a></code> before,\nthat task will execute first. That being said, if you need to schedule task asynchronously, but\nas soon as possible, <code><a href=\"api/index/const/asap\" class=\"code-anchor\">asap</a></code> scheduler is your best bet.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"example\" translation-result=\"on\">例子<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/index/const/asapScheduler#example\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"example\">Example<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/index/const/asapScheduler#example\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">比較非同步和越快越好排程器&#x3C;</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Compare async and asap scheduler&#x3C;</p>\n\n<code-example language=\"ts\">\nimport { <a href=\"api/index/const/asapScheduler\" class=\"code-anchor\">asapScheduler</a>, <a href=\"api/index/const/asyncScheduler\" class=\"code-anchor\">asyncScheduler</a> } <a href=\"api/index/function/from\" class=\"code-anchor\">from</a> 'rxjs';\n\nasyncScheduler.schedule(() => console.log('async')); // scheduling 'async' first...\nasapScheduler.schedule(() => console.log('<a href=\"api/index/const/asap\" class=\"code-anchor\">asap</a>'));\n\n// Logs:\n// \"<a href=\"api/index/const/asap\" class=\"code-anchor\">asap</a>\"\n// \"async\"\n// ... but '<a href=\"api/index/const/asap\" class=\"code-anchor\">asap</a>' goes <a href=\"api/index/function/first\" class=\"code-anchor\">first</a>!\n</code-example>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n  \n\n  \n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/deprecations\n - api/index\n - api/index/const/asap\n - api/index/const/asyncScheduler\n - api/index/function/generate\n - guide/scheduler\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/index\n - api/index/const/asap\n - api/index/const/asapScheduler#asapscheduler\n - api/index/const/asapScheduler#description\n - api/index/const/asapScheduler#example\n - api/index/const/asyncScheduler\n - api/index/function/first\n - api/index/function/from\n - https://github.com/reactivex/rxjs/edit/master/src/internal/scheduler/asap.ts?message=docs(index)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L55-L54\n - https://github.com/reactivex/rxjs/tree/7.5.2/src/internal/scheduler/asap.ts#L55-L54\n-->"
